  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>The Retirement Home is in chaos as the Old Folks have stopped taking their meds. </strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/cd00abdb094cf3d26adeb2698cdba3ac.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/cd00abdb094cf3d26adeb2698cdba3ac.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/cd00abdb094cf3d26adeb2698cdba3ac.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stop the onslaught of doctors from reaching the medicine cabinet and putting you all down for a nap. <br><br>Defend your retirement home with a cast of quirky Old Folks. Plan your defenses carefully and try different strategies with the variety of towers and upgrades.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/2051685471de67111f41184d0ec40084.webp?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/5b85bca966dbf8629eae7694d3277120.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/5b85bca966dbf8629eae7694d3277120.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/5b85bca966dbf8629eae7694d3277120.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each offensive tower you can place down is a different Old Folk each with their own strengths and weaknesses. <br><br><strong>Granny</strong> - Smacks the doctors with her trusty cane.<br><br><strong>Gramps</strong> - Throws slippers at the whippersnapper doctors with deadly accuracy.<br><br><strong>Poopy Pops</strong> - Poisons enemy doctors with his stinky fart attacks.<br><br><strong>Storytime Sally</strong> - Slows down enemies with her boring stories about the good old days.<br><br><strong>Crazy Carl</strong> - Throws explosive potions dealing splash damage.<br><br><strong>Boxer Bob</strong> - Throws heavy punches but has Alzheimer's and sometimes stuns nearby Old Folks.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/4c0c3c8328a58f99973c3c8a7e9d09f5.webp?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from 7 uniquely designed levels. Change your strategy to suit each map and stop the doctors at all costs.<br><br>Levels:<br><br><strong>The Lounge</strong><br><br><strong>The Cafeteria</strong><br><br><strong>The Garden</strong><br><br><strong>The Hospital</strong><br><br><strong>The Basement</strong><br><br><strong>The Bingo Hall</strong><br><br><strong>The Swimming Pool</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/c4a4add1ea9c2ffe29f279b4bebb2659.webp?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/2db0498ac29fcbd5422a025f9af90917.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/2db0498ac29fcbd5422a025f9af90917.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/2db0498ac29fcbd5422a025f9af90917.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Watch the mayhem increase as you upgrade your Old Folks in hilarious ways to deal with more devastating enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/e3f9eddbe38897f16700ed76be8d15f7.webp?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/ec29899ee7e74167ecd8f29cd47564d7.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/ec29899ee7e74167ecd8f29cd47564d7.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/ec29899ee7e74167ecd8f29cd47564d7.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from 4 support towers designed to support your Old Folks in unique ways. <br><br><strong>Meds Vending Machine</strong> - Dispenses \"special\" medications to nearby Old Folks which will get them feeling like they are 20 all over again, increasing their attack speed.<br><br><strong>Heater</strong> - Keep the nearby Old Folks bones warm and prevent them getting sick and stopping their attacks as often.<br><br><strong>Kamikaze Scooter </strong>- When things are desperate send a \"Kamikaze Scooter\" down the path to knock down the doctors in a high speed rampage.<br><br><strong>Bake Sale Stall</strong> - Sell \"Grandma's Baking\" to the passing doctors to earn passive income.<br><br><br><strong>More levels, old folks and doctor enemies coming soon!</strong>",
