ses. <br><br><strong>Granny</strong> - Smacks the doctors with her trusty cane.<br><br><strong>Gramps</strong> - Throws slippers at the whippersnapper doctors with deadly accuracy.<br><br><strong>Poopy Pops</strong> - Poisons enemy doctors with his stinky fart attacks.<br><br><strong>Storytime Sally</strong> - Slows down enemies with her boring stories about the good old days.<br><br><strong>Crazy Carl</strong> - Throws explosive potions dealing splash damage.<br><br><strong>Boxer Bob</strong> - Throws heavy punches but has Alzheimer's and sometimes stuns nearby Old Folks.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/4c0c3c8328a58f99973c3c8a7e9d09f5.webp?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.poster.avif?t=1722277989\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.webm?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/db4a4e0642b4705e48065eb2b290ccdb.mp4?t=1722277989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from 7 uniquely designed levels. Change your strategy to suit each map and stop the doctors at all costs.<br><br>Levels:<br><br><strong>The Lounge</strong><br><br><strong>The Cafeteria</strong><br><br><strong>The Garden</strong><br><br><strong>The Hospital</strong><br><br><strong>The Basement</strong><br><br><strong>The Bingo Hall</strong><br><br><strong>The Swimming Pool</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/c4a4add1ea9c2ffe