y Old Folks bones warm and prevent them getting sick and stopping their attacks as often.<br><br><strong>Kamikaze Scooter </strong>- When things are desperate send a \"Kamikaze Scooter\" down the path to knock down the doctors in a high speed rampage.<br><br><strong>Bake Sale Stall</strong> - Sell \"Grandma's Baking\" to the passing doctors to earn passive income.<br><br><br><strong>More levels, old folks and doctor enemies coming soon!</strong>",
